<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span><span class="c5">زنا:</span> الزنا: معروف، يمد ويقصر.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>قال <span class="c2">(الشاعر)</span> :<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>